{"tid":1745481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網傳「以首3小時投票計算選舉結果」 選舉處：絕無此事","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T08:46:21.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43ecdc7ffd9434ccdf9157b1adbe966700a48dd8","tid":1745481,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"就網上流傳指投票站若在區議會選舉投票日，開放首3小時後無法繼續運作，選舉事務處會以投票首3小時的選票數目計算選舉結果，選舉處今日（22日）強調絕無此事，並澄清如下：<br />\n<br />\n11月24日（星期日）為區議會選舉投票日。一般投票站的投票時間為上午7時30分至晚上10時30分，總投票時數為15小時。<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉處強調，不會在選區整個投票未完成前計算該選區選舉結果</span>。<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉投票日當天，若某投票站因突發事件無法運作，而投票可於1.5小時內恢復，該投票站的開放時間會於同一日作相應延長。若投票站未能於1.5小時內恢復運作，該投票站的投票會押後至後備投票日，即12月1日（星期日）。<br />\n<br />\n如投票需要押後至12月1日，票站主任會把已上鎖及封妥的投票箱及一切相關文件，在候選人或代理人的見證下妥為封存，待12月1日再繼續用以投票。後備投票日當天，有關投票站開放時間以之前宣布停止運作的時間起計，至晚上10時30分結束，例如，若某投票站投票在11月24日上午10時30分停止運作，該投票站會在12月1日上午10時30分重新開放，至同日晚上10時30分，整個投票時數維持在15小時。<br />\n<br />\n選民在11月24日領取選票時，選舉處會在投票站內選民登記冊上該選民的記項劃線，以茲識別，故選民不能在後備日（12月1日）重複投票。<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處發言人說，如大批選民集中同一時段投票，個別票站有機會出現人龍。票站人員會盡快為選民服務，請大家忍讓及耐心等候。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191122/s00001/1574410759029/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191122%2Fs00001%2F1574410759029%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=07cb646a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191122%2Fs00001%2F1574410759029%2F&h=a1d80570\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191122/s00001/1574410759029/</a>"},{"pid":"f3e5ecc6f283dc46e20cc6dd8b66c1f16c4c520e","tid":1745481,"uid":303677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1401295bbb617be2190fc629d20ff6682b784e71","tid":1745481,"uid":232185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"仲乜依排咁興澄清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf319134afc674c61db3b6bc150371b67bbd80b","tid":1745481,"uid":300679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:45:35.000Z","msg":"主動回應多數都係會有事發生 記得早啲投"},{"pid":"3b25dab6bd5d31cf3905fe234c42855dc931d14a","tid":1745481,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=5166af06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=64d987c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"f6cef9e7cf7197c977fc2993aca9e42002333c0d","tid":1745481,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1401295bbb617be2190fc629d20ff6682b784e71","tid":1745481,"uid":232185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"仲乜依排咁興澄清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:46:21.000Z","msg":"正苦派多咗人mon post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}